  "description": "<p>This advanced climbing shoe excels on thin faces, pocket climbs, and in the gym. Its asymmetrical shape, superbly tensioned rands and down-cambered, curved last provide great power for edging. The down-lasted toe and power hinge under the arch help the Miura flex and grab small footholds.</p><ul><li>Made of suede leather with a full sewn-in 8-panel Dentex lining to limit stretch</li><li>1.1mm Laspoflex midsole in the toebox supports your foot to help reduce foot fatigue</li><li>Speed lace system pulls tight easily and cinches your foot for a great fit</li><li>Durable 4mm Vibram \u00aeXS Edge\u2122 sole grips even the tiniest foot holds</li><li>La Sportiva suggests downsizing 1-1.5 sizes (performance fit) or 0.5-1 sizes (comfort fit) from your street shoe size</li></ul>",
